MissingMoney

MissingMoney

Search Alert

No-cost lookup tool

A quick search could identify money that may already belong to you

MissingMoney provides a free way to check whether dormant funds, credits, refunds, or other unclaimed property may be tied to your records. The process is simple, practical, and designed to help you see where funds may be held and what steps are needed next.

FREE

Search first, figure out the path second

Start with a free search to check for possible funds linked to your name and your last known state. If there is a match, the tool helps explain where the money may be held and how a claim can be pursued.

What the tool helps you do

Look for potential unclaimed money held by states or financial institutions, review possible matches, and understand the claiming process without paying to begin.

LOOK UP
FUNDS

NEXT
STEPS

Clear results, useful guidance

Not every search leads to funds, but checking is fast and low effort. When records are available, MissingMoney points you toward the agency or holder involved so the process feels more manageable and credible.

Simple next step

Search by your name and last known state to see whether unclaimed funds may be waiting and how to claim what is yours.

Search for My Money

MissingMoney exists to make a confusing problem easier to navigate. Unclaimed funds can come from ordinary situations such as closed accounts, refunds, dividends, deposits, or checks that never reached their intended owner. The value of the service is not in hype, but in giving people a clear place to start.

The offer is straightforward: a free search tool that helps identify possible unclaimed money and shows where it may be held. For people who have moved, changed banks, or simply lost track of old records, that kind of practical visibility can turn uncertainty into a useful next step.

MissingMoney’s role is to support a process that feels official, grounded, and manageable. Instead of asking people to guess where to check, the service helps organize the search so eligible recipients can move from possibility to action with more confidence.

--==rail-51248082_HtmlBoundary_nmeo1hxjfpljnq0xb
